    {
      "text": "AV Jiu Ji Ma Jiang II (AV究極麻將2), also known as AV Kyuukyoku Mahjong 2 is an adult versus Mahjong game developed by Hummer Team and released by Ge De Industry Co. around 1995. It is a backport of Dial Q wo Mawase (ダイヤルQをまわせ！), an unlicensed Sega Mega Drive title.",
